Chris Webster is a Music Scene local singer/songwriter. She is a member of Mumbo Gumbo and has released 3 solo albums  Drive (1995), Now Playing (2002), and Something in the Water (2006?)  and one album with Cassie Webster and Scott Nygaard called Ten Thousand Miles. Now Playing was recorded live at the old Palms Playhouse (...and at The International Music Hall and Bistro in Grass Valley, CA).

